<Window x:Class="LambovaT_TeaApp.AboutUs"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:LambovaT_TeaApp"
        xmlns:materialDesign="http://materialdesigninxaml.net/winfx/xaml/themes"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Title="AboutUs" 
        Height="550" 
        Width="800"
        ResizeMode="NoResize"
        Background="#DBCBEA">
    <ScrollViewer CanContentScroll="True" 
                  VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Visible">
        <Grid>
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="58"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="87"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2" 
                   HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                   Height="58" 
                   Stroke="#76AA08" 
                   Fill="#C3E58D"
                   VerticalAlignment="Top" 
                   Width="800"/>
            <Label Content="Purple Tea"
                   FontSize="22"
                   Foreground="#503D75"
                   VerticalAlignment="Center"
                   HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                   FontFamily="SWScrps"
                   Margin="5,2,0,0" 
                   FontWeight="Bold" 
                   FontStyle="Normal"/>
            <Button Content="About us"
                    Grid.Column="0"
                    Width="100"
                    Foreground="#76AA08"
                    Background="Transparent"
                    BorderBrush="Transparent"
                    VerticalAlignment="Center"
                    HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    Margin="688,0,0,0"
                    FontFamily="RomanD" 
                    FontWeight="Bold"
                    FontSize="12"
                    Click="AbUs"/>
            <Button Content="Anonymous tea"
                    Grid.Column="0"
                    Width="125"
                    Foreground="#76AA08"
                    Background="Transparent"
                    BorderBrush="Transparent"
                    VerticalAlignment="Center"
                    HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    Margin="563,0,0,0"
                    FontFamily="RomanD" 
                    FontWeight="Bold"
                    FontSize="12"
                    Click="PersTea"/>
            <Button Content="Bubble tea specifics"
                    Width="180"
                    Foreground="#76AA08"
                    Background="Transparent"
                    BorderBrush="Transparent"
                    VerticalAlignment="Center"
                    HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    Margin="383,0,0,0"
                    FontFamily="RomanD" 
                    FontWeight="Bold"
                    FontSize="12"
                    Click="BubbleTeaSpec" 
                Grid.Column="0" 
                    />
            <Button Content="Catalogue"
                    Grid.Column="0"
                    Width="105"
                    Foreground="#76AA08"
                    Background="Transparent"
                    BorderBrush="Transparent"
                    VerticalAlignment="Center"
                    HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                    Margin="278,0,0,0"
                    FontFamily="RomanD" 
                    FontWeight="Bold"
                    FontSize="12"
                    Click="Catalogue" 
                     />

            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
                   Grid.Column="0"
                   HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
                   Height="87" 
                   Stroke="#76AA08" 
                   Fill="#D9F2B1"
                   Grid.Row="2"
                   Grid.RowSpan="1"
                   VerticalAlignment="Top" 
                   Width="800"/>
            <Rectangle HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
                   Height="15" 
                   Stroke="Transparent" 
                   Fill="#B99CD5"
                   Grid.Row="2"
                   VerticalAlignment="Bottom" 
                   Width="800"/>
            <Canvas HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
			Height="45" 
			Grid.Row="2" 
			VerticalAlignment="Top" 
			Width="55"
            RenderTransformOrigin="0,0" 
                Margin="0,10,0,0"
            >
                <Image 
                Height="23"
                Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
                RenderTransformOrigin="0,0" Canvas.Left="34" Canvas.Top="16">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform/>
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="16.556"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
                <Image 
                Height="23"
                Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
                RenderTransformOrigin="0,0" Canvas.Left="11" Canvas.Top="20" Width="24">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform  />
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="-44.306"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
                <Image 
                Height="23"
                Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
                RenderTransformOrigin="0,0." Canvas.Left="20" Canvas.Top="16" Width="25">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform ScaleX="-1"/>
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="-16.816"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
            </Canvas>

            <Canvas HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
			        Height="60" 
			        Grid.Row="1" 
			        VerticalAlignment="Top" 
			        Width="90" 
			        Margin="6,10,0,0">
                <Image 
		        Height="40"
		        Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
		        RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5" Canvas.Left="30">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform/>
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="21.984"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
                <Image 
		        Height="40"
		        Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
		        RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5" Canvas.Top="19">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform/>
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="57.653"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
                <Image 
		        Height="40"
		        Source="https://uxwing.com/wp-content/themes/uxwing/download/nature-and-environment/green-leaf-icon.png" 
		        RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5" Canvas.Left="60" Canvas.Top="20">
                    <Image.RenderTransform>
                        <TransformGroup>
                            <ScaleTransform/>
                            <SkewTransform/>
                            <RotateTransform Angle="67.054"/>
                            <TranslateTransform/>
                        </TransformGroup>
                    </Image.RenderTransform>
                </Image>
            </Canvas>

            <Label Content="About Us"
               Foreground="#503D75"
               VerticalAlignment="Top"
               HorizontalAlignment="Center"
               Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
               Grid.Row="1"
               Margin="0,20,0,0"
               FontSize="50"
               FontFamily="SWScrps"
               FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <Rectangle Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
                   Grid.Column="0"
                   HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                   Height="650" 
                   Stroke="#D9F2B1" 
                   Fill="#D9F2B1"
                   Grid.Row="1"
                   Grid.RowSpan="1"
                   VerticalAlignment="Top" 
                   Width="750"
                   Margin="0,110,0,50"/>
            <Label Content="History"
               Foreground="#76AA08"
               VerticalAlignment="Top"
               HorizontalAlignment="Left"
               Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
               Grid.Row="1"
               Margin="40,120,0,0"
               FontSize="35"
               FontFamily="SWScrps"
               FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <Label Content="Manager"
               Foreground="#76AA08"
               VerticalAlignment="Top"
               HorizontalAlignment="Right"
               Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
               Grid.Row="1"
               Margin="0,450,40,0"
               FontSize="35"
               FontFamily="SWScrps"
               FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
                   Height="270" 
                   Margin="40,175,0,0" 
                   Grid.Row="1" 
                   TextWrapping="Wrap" 
                   VerticalAlignment="Top" 
                   Foreground="#3E6328"
                   FontFamily="RomanD"
                   TextAlignment="Justify"                   
                   Width="710"><Run Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="Purple Tea is a quaint tea shop located in the heart of Sofia, Bulgaria. It was founded in the early 1900s by a young woman named Maria, who had a deep passion for tea and wanted to share her love for it with the world. Maria spent several years travelling across Asia, learning about different tea blends and perfecting her craft before returning to Bulgaria and opening her own tea shop. "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="Initially, Purple Tea was a small establishment that only offered a limited selection of teas, but over time it grew in popularity and reputation. Maria's attention to detail and dedication to quality ensured that her tea shop became a go-to destination for tea enthusiasts from all over the city. "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="During the socialist regime in Bulgaria, the shop faced several challenges, but Maria's unwavering determination and resourcefulness helped it survive.  "/><LineBreak/><Run Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="After the regime, Purple Tea continued to thrive and became a cultural landmark of Sofia. In 1995, the shop was passed down to Maria's granddaughter, who continued her mother's legacy.  "/><LineBreak/><Run Language="en-gb" Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="Today, Purple Tea remains one of the oldest and most respected tea shops in Sofia, known for its wide selection of high-quality teas and warm, inviting atmosphere. It continues to attract visitors from all over the world who are eager to experience a piece of tea history. "/></TextBlock>
            <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
                   Height="230" 
                   Margin="40,510,0,0" 
                   Grid.Row="1" 
                   TextWrapping="Wrap" 
                   VerticalAlignment="Top"
                   TextAlignment="Justify"                   FontFamily="RomanD"
                   Foreground="#3E6328"
                   Width="710"><Run Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="The current manager of Purple Tea, Galina, is a tea connoisseur who has dedicated their life to the art of tea. She has an extensive knowledge of tea varieties and blends, and is always experimenting with new recipes to keep the shop's menu fresh and exciting. "/><LineBreak/><Run Language="en-gb" Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="In addition to her expertise in tea, Galina is also deeply committed to customer service. She strives to create a warm and welcoming atmosphere in the shop, and is always eager to chat with customers about their favorite teas and offer recommendations. "/><LineBreak/><Run Language="en-gb" Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="Galina has also embraced modern technology to help expand the shop's reach. She has established an online store and social media presence, making it easier for customers to purchase their favorite teas and stay up-to-date on new offerings and events. "/><LineBreak/><Run Language="en-gb" Text="&#x9;"/><Run Text="Despite these modern touches, Galina remains committed to maintaining the traditional charm of Purple Tea. She continues to brew tea the old-fashioned way, using loose-leaf tea and classic teapots and cups, ensuring that every cup of tea served at Purple Tea is a true experience.  "/></TextBlock>
        </Grid>
    </ScrollViewer>
</Window>
